summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2020 HIGHLAND RIDGE OPEN RANGE LIGHT 275RLS TRAVEL TRAILER.  THE CONTACT STATED THE DRIVER SIDE SLIDE FAILED TO RETRACT AND CLOSE.
